com.centonni.springboot.configuration.tool.common

Class AbstractSpringBootConfigurationCompletionProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centonni.springboot.configuration.tool.common.AbstractSpringBootConfigurationCompletionProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.netbeans.spi.editor.completion.CompletionProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SpringBootPropertiesConfigurationCompletionProvider, SpringBootYamlConfigurationCompletionProvider

    public abstract class AbstractSpringBootConfigurationCompletionProvider
extends Object
implements org.netbeans.spi.editor.completion.CompletionProvider
    The Spring Boot Configuration implementation of CompletionProvider. The entry point of completion support. It scans the classpath for META-INF/spring-configuration-metadata.json files, Then demarshalls the files into the corresponding ConfigurationMetadata classes and later in the query task scans for items and fills the CompletionResultSet.
    Author:
    Komi Serge Innocent <komi.innocent at gmail.com>
